7 is from aiue oka, 21 is from inue shinsuke. For anyone else that is looking for a name: take a screenshot of the japanese name and use something like yandex to OCR the characters then copypaste them into nhentai's search bar (remember to remove the spaces). If there aren't any results you can try looking up the artist's pixiv or whatever, find a doujin cover and reverse search that with saucenao. Alternative option: reverse search any of their images, on saucenao find the danbooru link in the top right corner of the results (brown cube icon), when you're there click on the artist's tag, then add doujinshi to the search bar and reverse search one of the images to find their title on nh.
